comment.body:
Oh sorry, I missed the above discussion. If they are using a lot of links appearing in Social Widget filter, I think it's better that users could use their own custom rules. `generichide` would affect other generic cosmetic rules in other filters too.

@Yuki2718 Sorry, what do you think about this site?

I'll revert the above commit since it doesn't make much sense to just make exceptions to one rule.

